Koga Shuko fell back, to the ground as the rocket struck him.

---

Anubis raised his launcher, firing a rocket off at Striker.

---

Hades stumbled backwards, firing off two laser bolts as he yelled, each off 
at Prowl.

---

Unitron raised both rifles, firing four blasts from each, all heading for 
Sniper.
